{
  "stem": "9311.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in 1941, of course, Hitler broke the pact.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and they-- they went after Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In 1939 up to 1941, I couldn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I couldn't study.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because they said that I'm a capitalist's daughter, which they were in 1970, not when I was born.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They didn't let me to do nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then I got--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the Russians from 1939 to 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I tried to belong to a group-- a youth group.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call it Komsomols.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from the Komsomols, from the youth, you're gonna be a real-- a real Communist, which I didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I liked the Communists just to survive and to get the job or to go to school, whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the doors, everything was closed for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went twice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all rejected me, even my friends, which I went to school together, Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said that I'm from a very fine family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I kept my nose high.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we were the top of our town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they think that I shouldn't belong to this group.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the third time I went-- which my mother insisted I should go-- and-- they accepted me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was about a few months before the Germans broke the pact with Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew that I had to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the first what Hitler comes, they killed the youth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, Hitler was already there in [? the Rovna, ?] which is close to Korzec.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's about two hours by car.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The whole family got together, and they decided that I should go over-- which it was the border.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was no man's land for many years between Poland and Russia-- but now it's open.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
